snippet.title: Dragon Age: Inquisition Official E3 2013 Teaser Trailer -- The Fires Above
snippet.description:
Dragon Age: Inquisition - Explore a vast, fantasy world at the brink of catastrophe in this next-generation action RPG. Your journey awaits. Learn more at: http://o.ea.com/15939
Welcome to Dragon Age: Inquisition, where your choices shape and drive the experience. You'll make your mark in an expansive, story-driven open world filled with complex characters, challenging combat and difficult decisions. This upcoming video game will be released in 2014.
